  <data key="d16">explicit_textual</data>
  <data key="d17">To love belongs to charity as charity . For, since charity is a virtue , by its very essence it has an inclination to its proper act. Now to be loved is not the act of the charity of the</data>
  <data key="d18">reviewed_doctrinal</data>
</edge>
<edge source="concept.charity" target="concept.god" id="edge.concept.charity.has_object.concept.god">
