  <data key="d16">explicit_textual</data>
  <data key="d17">the object of charity is not a sensible good , but the Divine good which is known by the intellect alone. Therefore the subject of charity is not the sensitive, but the intellective appetite , i.e. the will .</data>
  <data key="d18">reviewed_doctrinal</data>
</edge>
