  <data key="d16">explicit_textual</data>
  <data key="d17">ighbor which binds each one to be solicitous for his neighbor's spiritual welfare; so that if he persist in doing it he acts against charity . Yet there can be active scandal without sin on the part of the person scandalized , as stated above ( Article 1, Reply to Objection 4 ).</data>
  <data key="d18">reviewed_doctrinal</data>
</edge>
