  <data key="d15">st.ii-ii.q045.a002.resp</data>
  <data key="d16">explicit_textual</data>
  <data key="d17">which unites us to God , according to 1 Corinthians 6:17 : "He who is joined to the Lord, is one spirit." Consequently wisdom which is a gift , has its cause in the will , which cause is charity , but it has its essence in the intellect , whose act is to judge aright, as stated above ( I-II:14:1 ).</data>
