  <data key="d16">structural_editorial</data>
  <data key="d17">Three meanings have been given to the sin against the Holy Ghost . For the earlier doctors , viz. Athanasius (Super Matth. xii, 32), Hilary (Can. xii in Matth.), Ambrose (Super Luc. xii, 10), Jerome (Super Matth. xii), a</data>
