  <data key="d16">structural_editorial</data>
  <data key="d17">As stated above ( II-II:37:2 ), discord is a daughter of vainglory, because each of the disaccording parties clings to his own opinion, rather than acquiesce with the other. Now it is proper to pride and vainglory to see</data>
