  <data key="d16">structural_editorial</data>
  <data key="d17">The observance of holy days is no hindrance to those things which are ordained to man's safety, even that of his body. Hence Our Lord argued with the Jews , saying ( John 7:23 ): "Are you angry at Me because I have heale</data>
  <data key="d18">structural</data>
