  <data key="d16">explicit_textual</data>
  <data key="d17">While contention implies a contradiction of words, strife denotes a certain contradiction of deeds . Wherefore a gloss on Galatians 5:20 says that "strifes are when persons strike one another through anger ." Hence st</data>
