  <data key="d15">st.ii-ii.q045.a003.resp</data>
  <data key="d16">structural_editorial</data>
  <data key="d17">As Augustine says (De Trin. xii, 14), the higher part of the reason is the province of wisdom, while the lower part is the domain of knowledge . Now the higher reason according to the same authority (De Trin. xii, 7) "is</data>
  <data key="d18">structural</data>
</edge>
