  <data key="d8">II-II q.46 — Folly which is opposed to wisdom</data>
  <data key="d9">question</data>
  <data key="d10">contains_article</data>
  <data key="d11">st.ii-ii.q046.a003</data>
  <data key="d12">II-II q.46 a.3 — To which capital sin is it reducible?</data>
