  <data key="d16">structural_editorial</data>
  <data key="d17">As already stated ( Article 2 ), folly, in so far as it is a sin , is caused by the spiritual sense being dulled, so as to be incapable of judging spiritual things. Now man's sense is plunged into earthly things chiefly </data>
  <data key="d18">structural</data>
</edge>
